N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4202.2 - Meetings

State Regulations

Regular meetings of the commission shall be held monthly
at an office of the commission. Special meetings may be had at any time on the
call of the chairman or of any two members. Notes
